text: Konstantin Kalinovsky (born 3 September 1975) is a Belarusian skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1998 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Belarus Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1998 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
